data.description: YOUR NEW HOME AWAITS ON 1.3 ACRES IN LOST LAKE! Perfectly appointed on 1.3 wooded acres and just a short walk to Lost Lake, this home features 3 finished stories and 4,300 square feet of living space. Open concept living space with stunning cathedral ceilings give this home a real "wow" factor. The main floor features a grand, two story entrance along with a two story, stone fireplace. Kitchen boasts granite counter tops, granite backsplash, and new  appliances. Multiple sets of sliders off of the dining room and living room area on to the expansive deck that was built in 2015. Main floor master with numerous closets and an en suite master bathroom. Three Season room adjacent to the master also features a new hot tub. Split floor plan with 2 more bedrooms on the main floor. Upstairs you will find another bedroom and a bonus room that could easily be converted a 5th bedroom or home office. Walk out lower level is finished and serves as additional living space for your family. New 12x16 storage shed is also included. Watch deer and other wildlife pass you by from your own yard at this unique property. All while enjoying living in a private, gated community offering a large lake, tennis courts and other amenities.
